<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=1440">
    <title>BABATHE.COM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/babathe.css">
    <script src="../../js/library.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header></header>
    <section class="container"> 
        <div class="login-wrap">
            <div>
                <div class="form-area join-area">
                    <h2 class="page-title">회원가입</h2>
                    <p class="">김바바 님의 소개로 방문하셨군요. 가입 완료 후 1,000P를 바로 적립해 드립니다.</p>
                    <div class="form-wrap phone-verify">

                        <div class="step-left">
                            <h3><span class="num">01.</span> 휴대폰 본인인증 *</h3>
                            <div class="step-box">
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box">
                                            <input type="text" value=""  id="join1-1" placeholder="이름 입력"/>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box">
                                            <select id="join1-2">
                                                <option>내국인</option>
                                                <option>외국인</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box">
                                            <input type="text" value=""  id="join1-3" placeholder="생년월일 입력 (8자리)"/>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box">
                                            <select id="join1-4">
                                                <option>남자</option>
                                                <option>여자</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box"> 
                                            <input type="text" value=""  id="join1-5" placeholder="휴대폰 번호 입력 ('-'제외하고 숫자만 입력)"/>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box">
                                            <select id="join1-6">
                                                <option>통신사</option>
                                                <option>SKT</option>
                                            </select>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- 인증번호 입력 -->
                                <div class="form-row btn-row">
                                    <div class="form-col">
                                        <div class="form-box d-flex">
                                            <input type="text" id="certiCode1" placeholder="인증번호 입력" class="w-120">
                                            <span class="form-mid-txt">02:00</span>
                                            <button type="button" class="btn sm btn-form">인증번호 재전송</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="form-msg c-secondary">인증 시간이 경과했습니다. 인증번호 재전송을 통해 인증을 다시 진행해 주세요.</p>
                                <!-- // 인증번호 입력 -->

                                <div class="pers-idx-guide">
                                    <div class="acd-box">
                                        <div class="accordion-title">
                                            <div class="ttile">
                                                <div class="checkbox">
                                                    <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree1" checked>
                                                    <label for="certiAgree1">본인 인증을 위한 약관 모두 동의</label>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <button>열림</button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="accordion-panel">
                                            <div>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2"> 
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree1-1" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree1-1">(필수) 개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree1-2" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree1-2">(필수) 고유식별정보 처리 동의</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree1-3" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree1-3">(필수) 통신사 이용약관</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree1-4" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree1-4">(필수) 서비스 이용약관</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="btn-area">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn primary2">인증번호 전송</a>  <!-- 인증번호 전송 후 버튼명 확인으로 변경 필요 -->
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="step-right"><!-- 비활성시 class="disabled" 적용, 활성 시 class="disabled" 삭제,  -->
                            <h3><span class="num">02.</span> 기본정보 입력 *</h3>
                            <div class="step-box">
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-box">
                                        <input type="text" value="01012345678"  id="join2-1-1" readonly />  <!-- 자동 입력 -->
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-box">
                                        <input type="password" value=""  id="join2-1-2" placeholder="비밀번호 입력" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-box">
                                        <input type="password" value=""  id="join2-1-3" placeholder="비밀번호 확인" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <ul class="list-group dash">
                                    <li>영문, 숫자, 특수문자 포함 8자리 이상</li>
                                    <li>사용 가능한 특수문자는 ~!@#$%^&* 입니다.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="form-box">
                                        <input type="text" value=""  id="join2-1-4" placeholder="이메일 주소 입력 (@ 포함)" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <h3><span class="num">03.</span> 약관동의</h3>
                            <div class="step-box">
                                <div class="pers-idx-guide">
                                    <div class="acd-box">
                                        <div class="accordion-title">
                                            <div class="ttile">
                                                <div class="checkbox">
                                                    <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree2" checked>
                                                    <label for="certiAgree2">약관 모두 동의</label>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <button>열림</button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="accordion-panel">
                                            <div>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2"> 
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree2-1" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree2-1">(필수) 웹사이트 이용약관</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree2-2" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree2-2">(필수) 멤버십 이용약관</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree2-3" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree2-3">(필수) 개인정보처리방침</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree2-4" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree2-4">(선택) 장기 미접속 시에도 계정 유지<span>※ 미동의시 1년 미접속 회원탈퇴 전환 <span>※ 장기 계정 유지 동의 시 1,000P 증정</span></span></label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <div class="checkbox type2">
                                                            <input type="checkbox" id="certiAgree2-5" checked>
                                                            <label for="certiAgree2-5">(선택) 마케팅 정보 수신 전체 동의</label>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a href="#" class="tx-link">보기</a>
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <div class="banner-area" style="background:#ddd; text-align:center; margin-top:20px; padding:20px 0;">배너이미지</div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="align-c">
                                <button type="button" class="btn lg primary">가입하기</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>